OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778490376
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after sawn-off
OL,4,Cshotgun found in his bedroom
OL,6,FAn Andover man who kept a sawn-off
OL,7,Fshotgun in his bedroom has been jailed
OL,8,Fafter pleading guilty to firearms and
OL,9,Fdrugs supply offences.
OL,11,FTeejay Stainer, 20, of Acre Court in
OL,12,FAndover, appeared before Winchester
OL,13,FCrown Court on Friday where he was
OL,14,Fsentenced to a total of eight and a
OL,15,Fhalf years.
OL,17,FThe court heard how on 12 November
OL,18,F2025, a sawn-off shotgun, pistol,
OL,19,Fcartridges and bullets were found in
OL,20,FStainer's home address during a
OL,21,Fwarrant.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
