OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778490376
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after sawn-off
OL,4,Cshotgun found in his bedroom
OL,6,FThe weapons, which also included a
OL,7,Fhammer, were in a Nike bag in
OL,8,FStainer's bedroom. A dagger was also
OL,9,Ffound in the kitchen.
OL,11,FOfficers searching the property also
OL,12,Ffound a bag containing Class A drugs
OL,13,Fand mobile phones with evidence of
OL,14,Fdrugs supply.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778490376
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after sawn-off
OL,4,Cshotgun found in his bedroom
OL,6,FStainer plead guilty to possession of
OL,7,Fprohibited weapons, possession of
OL,8,Fammunition without a firearms
OL,9,Fcertificate, and being concerned in
OL,10,Fthe supply of Class A and Class B
OL,11,Fdrugs, at Winchester Crown Court on 9
OL,12,FJanuary.
OL,14,FHe was today sentenced to five years
OL,15,Fin prison for the weapons offences,
OL,16,Fand two years for being concerned in
OL,17,Fthe supply of drugs to run
OL,18,Fconsecutively.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
