OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778490376
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after sawn-off
OL,4,Cshotgun found in his bedroom
OL,6,FStainer was on a suspended sentence
OL,7,Ffor robbery and received a further 18
OL,8,Fmonths as a result.
OL,10,FTrainee Detective Constable, Megan
OL,11,FLandeg, the OIC, said: "I welcome the
OL,12,Fresult from sentencing today, and am
OL,13,Fpleased that a dangerous criminal is
OL,14,Foff our streets.
OL,16,F"Tackling drug related harm is a
OL,17,Fpriority for Hampshire & Isle of Wight
OL,18,FConstabulary, as the supply of drugs
OL,19,Fis often linked to other offences such
OL,20,Fas violence, and the abuse of
OL,21,Fvulnerable adults and children.
OL,26,@sD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
