PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778490376
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after sawn-off
OL,4,Cshotgun found in his bedroom
OL,6,F"I hope this sentencing goes to show
OL,7,Fthat we will not tolerate offensive
OL,8,Fweapons or the supply of drugs in our
OL,9,Fcommunities. If you are involved in
OL,10,Fthis type of criminality, we will find
OL,11,Fyou and bring you to justice."
OL,13,FOther arrests as part of this
OL,14,Finvestigation:
